    • Method Detail

      • migrate

        void migrate​(Map<String,​String> values,
             Map<String,​String> defaultValues,
             Log log)
        This method is called before the String representations of Settings and values are parsed. Deprecated values should be removed from the values set Replacing values should be added to the values or defaultValues set, depending on desired migration
        Parameters:
        values - The map uses the name of settings as keys, and textual representation of values, as values
        defaultValues - The map uses the name of settings as keys, and textual representation of default values, as values
        log - The log to relay warnings about the use of deprecated Settings
